Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:10.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Cease what you are\Ndoing and gaze at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:14.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop everything, save for\Nthe thrumming of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:17.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Theft. It is an\Nespecially sweet vice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:19.21,Main,,0,0,0,,more elegant than vandalism
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:21.42,Main,,0,0,0,,and more complex\Nthan simple robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,A beautiful blend of secrets\Nand crime and mischief and fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.43,0:00:27.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Like dear Heathcliff,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:30.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I am defined by my\Nall-consuming passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:33.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Stealing is my greatest\Ncarnal pleasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,a pleasure for which\NI will risk my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:38.34,Main,,0,0,0,,a sexy prison from\Nwhich there is no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:41.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Why am I this way?\NWho can know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:44.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is the slave and\Nwho's the master?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:47.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Do divine eyes fall\Nupon me any longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,or have the given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:51.40,Main,,0,0,0,,The rush of a theft\Nallows me to forget all,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:55.20,Main,,0,0,0,,and yet to distantly\Nremember all, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:03.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Run and speak not.\NHide and run not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:05.35,Main,,0,0,0,,When you've found\Nme, punish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:09.32,Main,,0,0,0,,When you've punished\Nme, kill me. Save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Little boy, there is nothing\Nleft to steal from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:21.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You have long been an\Nempty shell. Just as I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:25.21,Main,,0,0,0,,And so, if you would gaze at\Nme, cease what you are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:29.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop everything save for the\Nthrumming of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:18.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:20.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Man, she's going to town!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:22.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Where do you think "there" is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:24.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. Like I'd know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:28.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you have work to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:33.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lieutenant Oscar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Do your job properly,\Nor I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:40.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:43.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lieutenant. Got it. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:50.30,Main,,0,0,0,,When did this place\Nbecome a pig farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Ooh, so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Squealing like a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Your terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:02.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna release you unless\Nyou agree to my terms first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You want more?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:05.39,Main,,0,0,0,,You've had plenty\Nof fun already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:09.25,Main,,0,0,0,,That was just a small perk.\NThieves are cheap rides.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, if you could croon\Nlike that Aiyan Meier,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I might consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:19.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Aiyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:22.31,Main,,0,0,0,,That famous masked\Nopera singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:26.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Aiyan is a soprano\Ndrammatico d'agilita.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:30.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Her voice has all the\Nrich fullness of a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:32.36,Main,,0,0,0,,But a tragic accident\Nleft most of her face
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:35.24,Main,,0,0,0,,burned beyond recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:38.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard some obsessed fan\Nwent crazy and attacked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:41.41,Main,,0,0,0,,After it happened, she began\Nwearing a mask onstage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:44.23,Main,,0,0,0,,for all of her performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:45.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Not just any mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.39,Main,,0,0,0,,This one's covered in gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:50.40,Main,,0,0,0,,It's worth more than the federal\Nbudget of a small country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Now there's a delicious rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:55.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it gets even juicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:59.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, the mask was given\Nto her as a courtship present
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,from a ghost haunting\Nthe Palais Gerniar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:04.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:09.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll lay out the terms\Nof our deal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:12.34,Main,,0,0,0,,First off, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this wise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, leaving a\Nnotorious thief in charge
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.40,Main,,0,0,0,,of guarding Aiyan's mask.\NI don't see how we can
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.27,Main,,0,0,0,,trust that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:36.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Every doll out there\Nis a double-crosser.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course we can't trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:41.33,Main,,0,0,0,,But the best way to catch\Na thief is with a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:43.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Those two will\Ntrip over each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.33,Main,,0,0,0,,and Lupin will fall\Ninto our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:00.24,Main,,0,0,0,,The architecture of the\NPalais Gerniar is as complex
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.37,Main,,0,0,0,,as it is ancient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:04.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I doubt if anyone who works\Nhere, save for my humble self,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.43,Main,,0,0,0,,of course, knows\Nall of its secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:07.39,Main,,0,0,0,,There are simply too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:12.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Up here on the roof\Nis where we keep our bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:15.43,Main,,0,0,0,,They produce honey, which\Nwe sell to famous suppliers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.30,Main,,0,0,0,,These are the aqueducts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:19.30,Main,,0,0,0,,They say water once flowed\Nthrough them to points
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:23.28,Main,,0,0,0,,all over the city, but as you\Ncan see, they're dry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm told that while\Nthe water still ran,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,it was called the\NRiver of Oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.40,Main,,0,0,0,,That's quite a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:32.33,Main,,0,0,0,,In reference to the river from\NGreek mythology. It washes away
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:35.42,Main,,0,0,0,,your past, allowing you\Nto forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:41.27,Main,,0,0,0,,And now we're backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:43.28,Main,,0,0,0,,"Don't be distracted\Nby shadows?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The ghost of Palais Gerniar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Legend has it, if you pay him\Nattention, he'll have power--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.25,Main,,0,0,0,,It's far more than a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:52.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It's quite true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:56.33,Main,,0,0,0,,The Palais itself has fallen\Nin love with the agilitá Aiyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Da Renzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.37,Main,,0,0,0,,This "Lupin the Third"\Nmay try to steal the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:04.41,Main,,0,0,0,,But if so, it will be the\Nlast thing he ever does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:08.38,Main,,0,0,0,,O Palais Gerniar,\Nplease forgive them their greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.31,Main,,0,0,0,,That's one creepy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.36,Main,,0,0,0,,That's Da Renzo, our carpenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:16.41,Main,,0,0,0,,People who work backstage in the\Ntheatre are a superstitious lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.40,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, allow me\Nto present Aiyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:29.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:46.39,Main,,0,0,0,,So Tosca is on\Nthe program tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:48.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The love story of a painter\Nand an opera singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:52.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a truly tragic tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Lady Tosca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Would it not be best\Nfor you to leave this place
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:06:59.26,Main,,0,0,0,,and return home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:00.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I must stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:02.42,Main,,0,0,0,,If I do not see him,\Nmy voice and heart will wither,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.27,Main,,0,0,0,,and I will never sing\Nsongs of love again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you have\Nhidden the traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Reveal him to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I know no traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Whatever do you mean, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Do not play the innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:17.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I know Angelotti\Nis here somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:34.30,Main,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:36.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Explain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Intruding upon me like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.38,Main,,0,0,0,,How can you expect me\Nto practice my singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, you see, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:47.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:52.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Lu--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Fujiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I've missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:57.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Running into you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It just feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I can guess why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:05.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You're after the mask,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Was that Lupin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Oscar! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.22,Main,,0,0,0,,The ghost of the Opera?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:42.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Tosca?! But I'm Tosca!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Aiyan? What are you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The devil himself\Nseeks to tear me apart
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:51.26,Main,,0,0,0,,from my darling Caravaggio!\NI beg you, have mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Even the devil himself\Nwould possess her heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:57.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Such is the power\Nof this prima donna!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:09:07.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[singing Puccini's\N"Vissi d'arte, vissi d'amore"]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:19.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[singing Puccini's\N"Vissi d'arte, vissi d'amore"]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Lupin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that how it goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.28,Main,,0,0,0,,They may have\Nadlibbed a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:48.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Aiyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.42,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the ghost's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.42,Main,,0,0,0,,He sent a message\Nwritten in blood because
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.22,Main,,0,0,0,,we have angered him tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all over now, Aiyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I should be well enough\Nto stand before the next song.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Have someone fill in for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:20.25,Main,,0,0,0,,But there's no one\Nwho can replace you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:24.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:28.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You got pretty much\Nthe same build.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:31.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Put on the fake mask\Nand no one will have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:32.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,What'd I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:42.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Knock 'em dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.29,Main,,0,0,0,,A cheap ride, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:47.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Then why do you keep\Ngroping me like a prize pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:48.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Cool it, doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just a pat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:52.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, live up to your part of\Nthe bargain and reel Lupin in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:55.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're not\Noverestimating this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:56.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Take it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,She's a good enough actress to\Nfake a pretty convincing orgasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:02.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, stay in costume--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I have the headpiece\Nfor Miss Aiyan's next
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.28,Main,,0,0,0,,costume change here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:13.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You just stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:15.26,Main,,0,0,0,,The stage manager\Nwill come fetch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! My dearest love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:21.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Why have you not\Ncome for me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:23.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Without you,\Nmy life is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I am nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:27.36,Main,,0,0,0,,She isn't half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:30.24,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the timing for\Nher switch with Aiyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It's right before\Nthe end of the act, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:34.37,Main,,0,0,0,,In about twenty minutes,\NI believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.26,Main,,0,0,0,,...Would that I could abandon\Nthis foolish jealousy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:38.29,Main,,0,0,0,,The stage elevator will\Nlower her down to the cellar,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:40.38,Main,,0,0,0,,where the real Aiyan\Nwill be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:43.38,Main,,0,0,0,,A dramatic trap door\Nswitch beneath the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:46.26,Main,,0,0,0,,The thieves won't be able to\Nresist that kinda opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:48.39,Main,,0,0,0,,to snatch the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujiko may or may\Nnot trip him up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:52.33,Main,,0,0,0,,down there but when\Nshe's done with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:55.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Lupin won't be walking\Nstraight, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:56.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,We have officers\Nin place, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Something's up.\NIt's not time to change yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.36,Main,,0,0,0,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What the--?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:52.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[Aiyan singing Puccini's\N"Vissi d'arte, vissi d'amore"]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:54.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Aiyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:00.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:02.41,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't how we planned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:12.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:14.38,Main,,0,0,0,,"Go to the fifth spike\Nmark from the right"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:18.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:21.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It was all a set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:24.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Somebody used the prop\Nletter to get Aiyan to move
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.35,Main,,0,0,0,,to the right spot on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Her life was never in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,It was only meant to look\Nlike someone wanted her dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:33.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:48.42,Main,,0,0,0,,So, that means the ghost\Nof the Opera is--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:50.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Lupin the Third.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:52.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I will stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:56.32,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter what it takes, I won't\Nlet you touch Aiyan's mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:01.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I am coming to you, my beloved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.37,Main,,0,0,0,,We shall be\Ntogether again soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:07.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Aiyan is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Aiyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, pal,\Nyou can't have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:13.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I know that voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:22.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Are those--?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:24.28,Main,,0,0,0,,They're the bees\Nwe keep up on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Where do you little rascals\Nthink you're going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:35.22,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:36.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow! They're stinging me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.22,Main,,0,0,0,,--It hurts, it hurts, it hurts!\N--No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:40.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You mustn't take off the mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I planted a device\Nin the headpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It makes this sound\Nthat bees just can't resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Pretty nifty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute,\Nthat's not Aiyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's Nora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,She was working here\Nas a prop mistress
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,up until five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Da Renzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Alrighty, then,\Njust one thing left to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Get my hands on that mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:17.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Zenigata!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You go after the guy\Nin the cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:31.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.33,Main,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Lock-picking is so beneath me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,It's tedious grunt work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:47.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Do your part, pig lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.38,Main,,0,0,0,,"Pig lady"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:55.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Run like your bacon\Ndepends on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:58.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Think you can lay off\Nthe pig comparisons?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:15:59.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.23,Main,,0,0,0,,"Spittoon," then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.20,Main,,0,0,0,,"Spittoon"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:04.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but\Na receptacle for male lust.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:07.24,Main,,0,0,0,,That's all you're good for,\Nyou worthless piece of trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:10.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,That way, Spittoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:17.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:19.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:21.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.23,Main,,0,0,0,,At last, we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.31,Main,,0,0,0,,It's been too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,You dirty rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:34.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You're persistent, Zenigata,\NI'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.36,Main,,0,0,0,,But what about the mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:36.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.37,Main,,0,0,0,,The mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't give a damn about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm here to settle the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:43.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:44.35,Main,,0,0,0,,My good tie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:49.26,Main,,0,0,0,,O Zenigata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:51.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Wherefore art thou, Zenigata?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:55.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Wherefore am I Zenigata?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:17:00.41,Main,,0,0,0,,'Tis 'cause the very blood\Nin my veins cries out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.40,Main,,0,0,0,,To stamp out the\Nentire line of Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm told that while\Nthe water still ran,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.27,Main,,0,0,0,,it was called the\NRiver of Oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:21.37,Main,,0,0,0,,That's quite a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:24.33,Main,,0,0,0,,In reference to the river\Nfrom Greek mythology.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It washes away your\Npast, allowing you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,to forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:54.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I carry the Zenigata family\Nname, and you the name
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:56.41,Main,,0,0,0,,of a thief!\NBlood will always tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:59.20,Main,,0,0,0,,It's blood you want, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:00.26,Main,,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:03.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh- I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:07.35,Main,,0,0,0,,A lovely red sauce mixed with\Na touch of chili powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:10.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll give you\Nsome extra, on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:14.31,Main,,0,0,0,,It's in my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.36,Main,,0,0,0,,They're burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I got turned around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.35,Main,,0,0,0,,How did I end up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:22.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Your blood-soaked form!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,So horrible,\Nand yet so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:26.32,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:27.34,Main,,0,0,0,,None of that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:29.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:32.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't let gooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Da Renzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:36.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:38.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,But now that you know the secret\Nof the Opera ghost, I must!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:53.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Th--there's another\Nghost in the Opera?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:00.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Da Renzo wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Aiyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:04.24,Main,,0,0,0,,My love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:06.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Da Renzo, we'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:08.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, Aiyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:23.42,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't the kind of room you\Nexpect to find in the catacombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:27.26,Main,,0,0,0,,That couch is made out\Nof one of the stone tombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:28.40,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nice, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,It's very avant-garde.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,So, you two have been living\Ndown here all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:39.38,Main,,0,0,0,,You see, it felt like the entire\Nworld was opposed to our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.33,Main,,0,0,0,,If it meant I could be\Nwith him, I was willing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:48.39,Main,,0,0,0,,to give up everything; my name,\Nmy career, even my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:53.39,Main,,0,0,0,,When I realized that the prop\Nmistress, Nora, had real talent
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:58.42,Main,,0,0,0,,as a singer, I began training\Nher to take my place as Aiyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:03.21,Main,,0,0,0,,And then, One day, it was time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on, you mean you\Ndid that to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:06.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It burned a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Even so, it was worth it\Nto be with the love of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:14.42,Main,,0,0,0,,My dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:16.32,Main,,0,0,0,,What a perfect plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:19.36,Main,,0,0,0,,In one stroke, we made Nora's\Ndreams come true and made sure
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:22.31,Main,,0,0,0,,no one would ever\Nbother us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:23.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What could anyone suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:26.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Aiyan was still on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:29.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You chose to live\Nfor love, instead of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.29,Main,,0,0,0,,What I don't understand is how\Nyou could leave that gorgeous
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:37.38,Main,,0,0,0,,opera house to live in a\Ndisgusting old crypt like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.32,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's not a crypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:42.28,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the most\Nstimulating stage there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.40,Main,,0,0,0,,The stage of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,This mask is no use to us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:49.21,Main,,0,0,0,,We could sell it and\Nbuy a house somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.35,Main,,0,0,0,,This thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:57.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I would rather use it\Nto heat up the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.35,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:05.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it'll be a lot less\Nvaluable burned to a crisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:07.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:08.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, another guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:10.24,Main,,0,0,0,,How lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:11.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:12.30,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:14.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you two like\Nto join us for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.35,Main,,0,0,0,,We would love to.
